Default logic reasoning by reduction to SAT
-------------------------------------------

We (Dominik and Zeno) wrote this program as an exercise for the lecture
"Knowledge Representation and Reasoning" at Uni Freiburg, given by Bernhard
Nebel, Stefan Wölfl, and Jussi Rintanen.
http://www.informatik.uni-freiburg.de/~ki/teaching/ws0405/krr/

The program needs zchaff, which used to be non-free.
Instead, one could also call a free solver, e.g. MiniSAT.

http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Default_logic

Sorry, the rest of the documentation is in German.

